* Chelsie Preston Crayford as Gwen EPISODES
BROADCAST Section::::Broadcast .
The first three episodes debuted in Australia on 28 January as a single 90-minute telemovie .
Subsequent episodes of the ten - episode series were released daily until 4 February 2018 .
It debuted on Netflix worldwide on April 28 , 2018 .
